  "detailed_description": "<h1>🔮 THE HEART OF THE TEMPORAL RIFT</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Welcome to <i>Singularity</i> — a quantum breach in reality.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This isn’t just a skill. It’s the <i>core</i> of CYBERSLAYER.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this world, you don’t just fight — you <i>refuse to die</i>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When everything falls apart, trigger Singularity and <i>tear through time</i>. Instantly rewind to a moment before the strike, before the fall, before the fatal mistake.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leave a trail of broken chronology as you defy fate itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >More than a perk. It’s a philosophy of survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are not immortal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>You are the glitch in the system.</strong></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SLIDE — SPEED AS A WEAPON</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glide through danger with a razor-sharp slide. Close distance, dodge death, and turn momentum into destruction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/f41d04aed9357702493216df323d9314.poster.avif?t=1753960225\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/f41d04aed9357702493216df323d9314.webm?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/f41d04aed9357702493216df323d9314.mp4?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SINGULARITY — TEAR THROUGH TIME</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break the timeline. Activate the Singularity perk to rewind your fate — step back through fractured time and rewrite the moment of impact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/34ff7e7937c7b0165e8292385f9d3709.poster.avif?t=1753960225\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/34ff7e7937c7b0165e8292385f9d3709.webm?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/34ff7e7937c7b0165e8292385f9d3709.mp4?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WEAPON THROW — STYLE KILLS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Launch your blade with lethal precision, then leap into action. Chain it with parkour to create your own rhythm of violence. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/16e3743e35209056d6e2358020b531b8.poster.avif?t=1753960225\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/16e3743e35209056d6e2358020b531b8.webm?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/16e3743e35209056d6e2358020b531b8.mp4?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EPIC FIRST-PERSON COMBAT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every strike hits like a shockwave. Slice, slam, and slaughter in visceral first-person battles that feel brutally close and personal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/67706c036f30aaa0d104a43abedea1b7.poster.avif?t=1753960225\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/67706c036f30aaa0d104a43abedea1b7.webm?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/67706c036f30aaa0d104a43abedea1b7.mp4?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CYBERSLAYER is a ruthless first-person action slasher that immerses you in the adrenaline-fueled rhythm of a cyberpunk future. You must overcome deadly trials within a giant megastructure, the last refuge of humanity after a global cataclysm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resources are running out, and the only sanctuary for survivors has turned into an arena for a merciless struggle for existence. The final battle is inevitable—its outcome will determine whether humanity has a future or faces total annihilation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features <strong>over 5 diverse and colorful levels</strong>, where you must <strong>race against time</strong>. Your arsenal consists of <strong>only melee weapons</strong>, but that doesn’t mean the fight will be easy. You can <strong>throw your weapons at enemies</strong> or <strong>engage in brutal close combat</strong>, creating your own combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All of this is accompanied by an <strong>unforgettable soundtrack</strong> that will fully immerse you in the cyberpunk world. Show no mercy. Spare no one. Only the fastest, most brutal, and most relentless will survive.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SLIDE — SPEED AS A WEAPON</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glide through danger with a razor-sharp slide. Close distance, dodge death, and turn momentum into destruction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/f41d04aed9357702493216df323d9314.poster.avif?t=1753960225\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/f41d04aed9357702493216df323d9314.webm?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/f41d04aed9357702493216df323d9314.mp4?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SINGULARITY — TEAR THROUGH TIME</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Break the timeline. Activate the Singularity perk to rewind your fate — step back through fractured time and rewrite the moment of impact.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/34ff7e7937c7b0165e8292385f9d3709.poster.avif?t=1753960225\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/34ff7e7937c7b0165e8292385f9d3709.webm?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/34ff7e7937c7b0165e8292385f9d3709.mp4?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WEAPON THROW — STYLE KILLS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Launch your blade with lethal precision, then leap into action. Chain it with parkour to create your own rhythm of violence. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/16e3743e35209056d6e2358020b531b8.poster.avif?t=1753960225\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/16e3743e35209056d6e2358020b531b8.webm?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/16e3743e35209056d6e2358020b531b8.mp4?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>EPIC FIRST-PERSON COMBAT</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every strike hits like a shockwave. Slice, slam, and slaughter in visceral first-person battles that feel brutally close and personal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/67706c036f30aaa0d104a43abedea1b7.poster.avif?t=1753960225\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/67706c036f30aaa0d104a43abedea1b7.webm?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3536100/extras/67706c036f30aaa0d104a43abedea1b7.mp4?t=1753960225\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CYBERSLAYER is a ruthless first-person action slasher that immerses you in the adrenaline-fueled rhythm of a cyberpunk future. You must overcome deadly trials within a giant megastructure, the last refuge of humanity after a global cataclysm.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Resources are running out, and the only sanctuary for survivors has turned into an arena for a merciless struggle for existence. The final battle is inevitable—its outcome will determine whether humanity has a future or faces total annihilation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features <strong>over 5 diverse and colorful levels</strong>, where you must <strong>race against time</strong>. Your arsenal consists of <strong>only melee weapons</strong>, but that doesn’t mean the fight will be easy. You can <strong>throw your weapons at enemies</strong> or <strong>engage in brutal close combat</strong>, creating your own combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >All of this is accompanied by an <strong>unforgettable soundtrack</strong> that will fully immerse you in the cyberpunk world. Show no mercy. Spare no one. Only the fastest, most brutal, and most relentless will survive.</p>",
